summary: Great convertible notebook at a great price.
description: Great for a cheap price! Get's the job done. It's nearly two years old and still works as good as new.

summary: Did not lasted as long as possible
description: ASUS computer died after about 2 years. It should hhave lasted as long as possible.

summary: Good enough
description: Met the purpose I bought it for. Am satisfied

summary: Great product, useful and good for travel with one serious power management flaw
description:
Very good Display, good Keyboard size and feel. Easy to use and great for travel. Why I dont give it 5 stars well one main reason:
If you unplug it and put it to sleep it drain the battery hella fast so it needs to be constantly plugged in or you have to always shut it down all the way then startup takes more time. My laptop can be in sleep mode for 3 days or a week and the battery will not die this one you leave it in sleep for 12 hours that is it its done.

summary: SUPER Excellent
description: Been using this for over a year. Had 2 friends get one. They love them. I believe it IS the best Tablet/Laptop on the market.

summary: Great product in theory
description: Great product in theory. Solid build, great price. I bought the 2GB RAM model, and honestly it just wasn't enough for what I wanted to do (internet surfing, netflix, gameboy emulators)
